<div class="quotes">
		<h2>Quotidian Acumen</h2>
			<div id="wp_quotes">
		<div class="wp_quotes_quote">Military men are dumb, stupid animals to be used as pawns for foreign policy.<br />
</div>
					<div class="wp_quotes_author">Henry Kissinger</div>
